      "raw_text": "PALOUSE, Jan. 24.-Eslick IL\nHartnell, who form the Palouse\nCity Construction company and\nwho have have been awarded the\ncontract to dig a tunnel near here\non the Spokane & Inland, are max\ning camp this morning and work\nwill commence at once. The tun-\nmel will be 600 feet long. Two\nhundred and fifty men will be en-\nployed."
    }
